name: ETH Printer
description: $ETHPrinter is here, and it’s ready to go brrr. Every sale feeds $ETHPrinter and is distributed directly to holders. This isn’t just another meme token—it’s your golden ticket to nonstop ETH rewards. The Base community has been waiting for a true $ETH printer, and it’s finally here. Grab your friends, load up your wallets, and join the $ETHPrinter movement. Because when we print, we print $ETH—forever. Misson: Build the biggest $ETHPrinter in the world on Base to onboard the next generation of Web3 users into the Ethereum and Base ecosystems. By combining community-driven tokenomics, advanced staking strategies, and direct $ETH distributions, we aim to democratize the benefits of Ethereum’s ecosystem growth.
